			>
			Poor implementation of good ideas is how I would classify both horror and the current version of SoD. <br>I am sad about the changes of SoD, getting my aa's back for something more useful isnt even exciting cause I love the idea behind SoD, yea its totally not worth the points in its current form, but I wish they would look into balancing it out.<br>Horror I also consider a bad implementation of a good idea, yes we need some dot or dots to combat the now increasingly fast fights that make up 99 percent of EQ, the refresh timer would have had its place when fights lasted 30+ mins on a raid and 1 to 2 mins at least in a group, but they do not now.
