<DIV></DIV>
<P>Ky, </P>
<P>I think you and Brenlo are missing the point.&nbsp; Necros may get back their AA "points", but we still lose an AA "ability".&nbsp; No one will re-purchase this ability, nor will anyone buy it in the future unless they have a large amount of&nbsp;AA points to blow (yes, I mean "blow"... i.e. waste).</P>
<P>I think we would rather have the AA in the orignal form (melee capability), rather than get our points back or have the cost modified.&nbsp; If this AA ability stays in it's current form, you may as well add it to the MULTIPLE other AA's that necros have that are completely WORTHLESS&nbsp; (Dead Mesmerization, Fearstorm, and MGB).&nbsp;&nbsp;</P>
<P>You should be concentrating less on getting our points back, and more on getting the ability reverted to it's earlier form.</P>
<P>Just my opinion.</P>
