			<P>The situation as it stands is unacceptable. The original SoD was underpowered, the nerfed version is useless.</P>
<P>Given that the SoD AA was considered balanced during the beta process (I remember reading about the mele dps on the public Necro boards after the NDA was lifted but before GoD went live), and that subsequently a developer felt that the mele dps was too much, one of the following should be done:</FONT></P>
<P>1. Return SoD to its original version since it was considered balanced during beta&nbsp;(I realize this won't happen since a dev's ego is now at stake).</FONT></P>
<P>2. Leave the SoD mele damage as it currently is but raise the range (bow) damage to compensate.</FONT></P>
<P>3. Leave the SoD mele and range damage as it is but lower the recast time to bring it in line with the DPS of other AAs of similar cost.</FONT></P>
<P>4. Lower the cost of SoD to 12 AAs to bring it in line with other low DPS AAs.</FONT></P>
<P>Ky we need more than a spokes person for SoE.&nbsp;We need an advocate for our class. I know you are doing what you can but understand that since you have started to try to communicate with us, we have had an existing ability nerfed and have not seen any of the issues we have raised resolved.</P>
