<DIV>Mage AA - Host of the Elements = 12 AA points, Refresh 22 min, Duration 30sec, approx 180dps burst (5400 dmg)</DIV>
<DIV>Necro AA - Swarm of Decay = 30 AA points, Refresh 30 min, Duration 60 sec, approx 27dps burst (1600 dmg)</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Looks to me like we need to get approximately 6x the damage out of this AA to make it comparable</DIV>
<DIV>to mage pets for damage / AA cost.&nbsp; We NEED some burst damage stuff!</DIV>
